Yep — this one had the same class of problems, plus a few new ones:
	•	smart quotes everywhere
	•	...spread replaced by unicode ellipsis
	•	invalid actors.map((*, i) syntax
	•	direct frontend call to Anthropic again
	•	FSelect used like it supports children when it doesn’t
	•	canvas code with smart quotes
	•	a few state/template merges that could create bad ids

